---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Home"
description: "A curated travel journal — exploring the world's most beautiful places through photography and storytelling."
---

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__media">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=1800&q=85&auto=format"
      alt="Majestic mountain landscape reflecting in a lake at golden hour"
      class="hero__img"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <p class="hero__eyebrow">A Journey Begins</p>
    <h1 class="hero__title">The World is a<br /><em>Beautiful Place.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">Exploring it, one frame at a time.</p>
    <a href="/journal/" class="btn btn--ghost">Read the Journal</a>
  </div>
  <p class="hero__scroll" aria-hidden="true">Scroll ↓</p>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ INTRO -->
<section class="intro">
  <div class="intro__inner">
    <p class="intro__text">
      From ancient cities to untouched wilderness — every journey tells a story worth sharing. Welcome to my corner of the world.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ LATEST POSTS FROM CMS -->
{% set posts = collections.journal %}
{% if posts.length > 0 %}
<section class="section latest-posts">
  <div class="section__inner">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2 class="section__title">Latest Adventures</h2>
      <a href="/journal/" class="section__link">View all →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">

      {# First post gets a wide hero card #}
      {% if posts[0] %}
      {% set p = posts[0] %}
      <a href="{{ p.url }}" class="card card--hero">
        {% if p.data.cover_image %}
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="{{ p.data.cover_image }}" alt="{{ p.data.cover_image_alt if p.data.cover_image_alt else p.data.title }}" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="card__body card__body--overlay">
          {% if p.data.region %}<span class="card__region">{{ p.data.region }}</span>{% endif %}
          <h3 class="card__title">{{ p.data.title }}</h3>
          {% if p.data.excerpt %}<p class="card__excerpt">{{ p.data.excerpt }}</p>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}

      {# Remaining posts in normal cards #}
      {% for p in posts | limit(5) %}
      {% if loop.index > 1 %}
      <a href="{{ p.url }}" class="card">
        {% if p.data.cover_image %}
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="{{ p.data.cover_image }}" alt="{{ p.data.cover_image_alt if p.data.cover_image_alt else p.data.title }}" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="card__body">
          {% if p.data.region %}<span class="card__region">{{ p.data.region }}</span>{% endif %}
          <h3 class="card__title">{{ p.data.title }}</h3>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ PLACEHOLDER GALLERY if no posts yet -->
{% else %}
<section class="section latest-posts">
  <div class="section__inner">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2 class="section__title">Latest Adventures</h2>
      <a href="/journal/" class="section__link">View all →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <a href="/journal/" class="card card--hero">
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528360983277-13d401cdc186?w=1200&q=80&auto=format" alt="Istanbul skyline at sunset" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card__body card__body--overlay">
          <span class="card__region">Turkey · June 2024</span>
          <h3 class="card__title">Where East Meets West</h3>
          <p class="card__excerpt">A city straddling two continents, alive with the call to prayer and the scent of spice markets.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/journal/" class="card">
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542051841857-5f90071e7989?w=800&q=80&auto=format" alt="Tokyo neon streets at night" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <span class="card__region">Japan</span>
          <h3 class="card__title">Tokyo After Dark</h3>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/journal/" class="card">
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539650116574-75c0c6d73f6e?w=800&q=80&auto=format" alt="Santorini white buildings and blue domes" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <span class="card__region">Greece</span>
          <h3 class="card__title">Santorini in Blue</h3>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/journal/" class="card">
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1476514525535-07fb3b4ae5f1?w=800&q=80&auto=format" alt="Swiss Alps snow-capped peaks" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <span class="card__region">Switzerland</span>
          <h3 class="card__title">Above the Clouds</h3>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/journal/" class="card">
        <div class="card__media">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517760444937-f6397edcbbcd?w=800&q=80&auto=format" alt="Desert dunes at sunset in Morocco" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <span class="card__region">Morocco</span>
          <h3 class="card__title">Sahara at Dusk</h3>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ PULL QUOTE -->
<section class="pullquote">
  <blockquote class="pullquote__text">
    "Travel is the only thing you buy that makes you richer."
  </blockquote>
</section>
